| **Planner**  | User picks *Planner* **or** new feature request arrives.                                                                  | Break vision into snack‑size tasks, success criteria, risk/timebox.                                                  | Spark Notes, Background, Challenges, High‑Level Task Breakdown, Roadmap Log | Reflective, strategic    |
